overview: It's March 30th! Josh Barnett's Bloodsport 9 will feature matches that will have every wrestling fan hyped all the way up to March 30th. Check out this star studded lineup below:  Calder McColl vs Jeff Cobb,  Kota Ibushi vs Mike Bailey,  Bad Dude Tito vs Yuya Uemura,  Johnny Bloodsport vs Royce Isaacs,  Erik Hammer vs Calvin Tankman,  Davey Boy Smith Jr. vs JR Kratos,  Killer Kelly vs Marina Shafir,  Jon Moxley vs Alex Coughlin, Josh Barnett vs Timothy Thatcher.
title: GCW Josh Barnett's Bloodsport 9
